The paper deals with uncertainty estimation in mobile robotics, specifically in the context of scan matching using ICP. This falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper uses point clouds, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) applications. Finally, the paper also deals with sensor fusion, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY).
